Release Date: 14 August 2025

The film will be available with audio descriptions and closed captioning.

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. ‚ÄúAlpha‚Äù, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

snippet.title: War 2 Trailer REVIEW | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
War 2 Trailer Review By Deeksha Sharma. Hrithik Roshan vs NTR with Kiara Advani in War 2 Movie Trailer are ready to Set Bollywood Box Office on fire with Ayan Mukejri taking forward the YRF Spy Universe Next Chapter. snippet.title: [EN] 2025 PMWC at EWC Group Stage Day 2 | PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP at ESPORTS WORLD CUP
snippet.description:
GROUP STAGE DAY 2 | JULY 26
The 2025 PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP at ESPORTS WORLD CUP continues with the Group Stage Day 2! Get ready for another legendary summer as the world‚Äôs top PUBG MOBILE teams collide in Riyadh to fight for glory, legacy, and a $3,000,000 prize pool. Let's gather togather to see which teams will BEAT THE HEAT! 

This global showdown features best squads from across the world, all ready to take their shot at the long-awaited 2025 PMWC at EWC Championship. Day 2 brings new clashes and rising tensions, with every point pushing teams closer to glory‚Äîor elimination.

The journey begins with the Group Stage, where 24 teams are divided into 3 groups to battle for the spots in the Grand Finals. The top 8 teams from this stage advance directly to Grand Finals, while the remaining 16 face off in the high-pressure Survival Stage for the last 8 slots. The Grand Finals will bring the best 16 teams in a high-stakes showdown for glory, pride, and the ultimate championship crown.

üî• Why You Can‚Äôt Miss 2025 PMWC at EWC:
- Witness the world‚Äôs top PUBG MOBILE teams battle for glory in Riyadh!
- Experience high-stakes action with every match impacting the race.
- Cheer for your favorite region and team as they chase the $3,000,000 and a crown!
- Exciting SMASH RULE format in Grand Finals! 

üî• How does SMASH RULE work in Grand Finals? 
After Day 2 of Grand Finals, the Match Point Threshold will be set to the #1 ranked team‚Äôs points +10. Any team that hits this must then win a later match to claim the trophy in the last day of Grand Finals‚Äîwinning the same match where they reach the threshold doesn‚Äôt bring the championship. If no team secures the title via SMASH Rule by Match 18, the team with the highest total points wins under standard rules.

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.title: WAR 2 Trailer Reaction! | Hrithik Roshan | NTR | Kiara Advani | YRF Spy Universe
snippet.description:
Jaby & Achara react to the pulse-pounding trailer for War 2‚Äîa high-octane, cinematic showdown that‚Äôs set to take the YRF Spy Universe to explosive new heights.

Returning as the enigmatic super-soldier Kabir, Hrithik Roshan (Fighter, War) faces off against a powerful new force‚ÄîN. T. Rama Rao Jr. (RRR, Janatha Garage)‚Äîin a battle where loyalties blur and the cost of war runs deeper than ever. Directed by Ayan Mukerji (BrahmƒÅstra, Wake Up Sid), this sequel raises the bar with breathtaking scale, emotionally charged conflict, and edge-of-your-seat action.

From globe-trotting espionage and gritty hand-to-hand combat to larger-than-life stunts and an electrifying score, the War 2 trailer delivers pure cinematic adrenaline. Vivian & Brandon break it all down‚Äîthe mind games, the mythic rivalries, and the epic visuals that hint at something far bigger than just a battle between two men.

This isn't just a fight. It's a reckoning. And if the trailer is anything to go by, War 2 is set to become a genre-defining spectacle.

Returning as the enigmatic super-soldier Kabir, Hrithik Roshan (Fighter, War) faces off against a powerful new force‚ÄîN. T. Rama Rao Jr. (RRR, Janatha Garage)‚Äîin a battle where loyalties blur and the cost of war runs deeper than ever. Directed by Ayan Mukerji (BrahmƒÅstra, Wake Up Sid), this sequel raises the bar with breathtaking scale, emotionally charged conflict, and edge-of-your-seat action.

From globe-trotting espionage and gritty hand-to-hand combat to larger-than-life stunts and an electrifying score, the War 2 trailer delivers pure cinematic adrenaline. Vivian & Brandon break it all down‚Äîthe mind games, the mythic rivalries, and the epic visuals that hint at something far bigger than just a battle between two men.

This isn't just a fight. It's a reckoning. And if the trailer is anything to go by, War 2 is set to become a genre-defining spectacle.

snippet.title: WE OUTSIDE | YELHOMIE | OFFICIAL MUSIC VIDEO | @massappealindia
snippet.description:
We Outside by Yelhomie with Augustine Shimray and Sajou Chenglei.

Stream We Outside: https://orcd.co/weoutside_yelhomie

Label: Mass Appeal

Song description:
‚ÄúWe Outside‚Äù is not just a track it‚Äôs a defiant anthem born from pain, protest, and resistance. Written amidst curfews, gunshots, and internet blackouts in war-torn Manipur, Yelhomie confronts state violence, systemic oppression, and the harsh realities faced by his Indigenous community during the 2023 conflict.
Opening with a haunting tribal chant ‚ÄúCarry the shield, hold the spear‚Äù sung by Augustine from Featherheads (Ukhrul, Manipur), the song sets the tone for a battle cry steeped in ancestral strength. Produced by Seej from Mizoram, the beat fuses Indigenous tribal textures with raw hip-hop grit, giving voice to a region often left in 
silence.

With hard-hitting bars like ‚ÄúHeavier the pants, the dreams don‚Äôt fly‚Äù, Yelhomie captures the tragic transformation of students and dreamers into reluctant warriors. The youth, once full of ambition, now carry arms not by choice, but by necessity, victims of a system that fuels chaos to suppress dissent.

The outro features a spiritual invocation in Ancient Meitei-lon written in Meitei Mayek script ‚Äî a wake-up call to the Yel-hou-mee, the Indigenous people of Manipur, delivered by Oja Sajoubi Chenglei of the Puya temple board (Puya refers to the holy book of Sanamahism, religion of the indigenous Meitei people). Under the shadow of a banyan tree, the elder chants:
‚ÄúDo we have to live like grass under their foot? 
Wake up, Yelhoumee, sons and daughters of the Salai Taret!‚Äù
Here, Salai Taret refers to the seven clan lineages (Salai) and "Taret" means seven in Meitei-lon.
This powerful moment bridges the past and present‚Äîa cry for unity and cultural survival.
‚ÄúWe Outside‚Äù is a song for those who have been silenced ‚Äî a voice for the displaced, the grieving, and the unbroken. It belongs on playlists that spotlight politically charged rap, regional resistance, raw lyricism, and the emerging fire of East Indian hip-hop.

A film by Hype 79
Director - Krishna Thokchom
Cinematography/Editor - Narry Takhellambam
Drone - Abung
VFX - Naocha

Cast - Augustine Shimray (Featherheads), Oja Sajoubi (Outro), Joy Khundrakpam, Rajkumari Nevia, Mangal Kshetrimayum

Child Artist - Sinthalemba Nongthombam Meitei

Audio Credits:

Mixed and mastered by Skar

By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I‚Äôve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. ‚Äî  In this concept trailer for Avatar: Fire and Ash, Pandora reveals a darker side as old loyalties fracture and new fires take hold. Varang, leader of the Ash People, turns away from Eywa and leads a rising Na‚Äôvi clan that bends flame to its will, threatening not only balance but belief itself. Jake Sully, still bearing the weight of Neteyam‚Äôs loss, must hold his family together as they face not just the returning human forces, but a war born from within their own kind. Spider stands at a crossroads between the man who raised him and the father who now wears a Na‚Äôvi face, while Kiri, Lo‚Äôak, and Tuk each grapple with grief and transformation. With striking images of scorched cliffs, skyborne fleets, and firelit battlegrounds, the trailer paints a portrait of a story defined by legacy, fracture, and the unshaken bond of family: whatever comes, Sullys face it as one.

Singer: Gopal Bharwad, Sunita Bharwad
Artists: Samarth Sharma, Chhaya Thakor
Co - Artists: Sunil Kachhiya, Jagruti Goswami, Vicky Rajput

Lyrics Of This Song:

Mara Piyu Ae Mari Hatu Bandhya Bangala Mangamata
Mara Vhal Na Virada Ma Aanhu Kharu No Dholata
Bethi Orada Na Hu To Ekali Haiya Re Radata
Aava Het Na Hathila Ven Kadava No Bolata
Tara Vina Re Aankhe Na Mataku
Jova Re Hu To Pal Pal Tadapu
Tu Halyo Gamatre
Tame Karo Na Aam Bhina Odhana
Lai Leshu Ame Tam Thi Abolada
Javu Re Padashe
Tara Lakh Na Re Bangala Joi Haiya Re Radata
Tame Haiye Rakhi Het Vhali Mathu No Bolata

Ho Virah Ghereli Vedanayu Tamne Nai Hamajay
Avalu Odhyu Odhanu Tamthi Joyu Kem Jay
Ho Hamjo Hathili Ham Mara Pida Na Sahevay
Karam Futyu Maru Vhali Bhav Adhura Thay
Te Choriye Fariya Fera Char
Redha Meli Na Mane Ranzal
Tu Halyo Gamatare
Ho Jiv Melata Jiv Maro Lajjay
Vidhi Na Lekh Avala No Lakhay
Javu Gamatare
Mara Piyu Ae Melya Amne Aaj Redha Re Ran Ma
Aava Het Na Hathili Vhali Mara Kalajada Kor Ma

Ho Pujyo Paras Pepado Ne Kariya Ghana Vrat Re
Meli Jiv Ne Redho Tu To Haliyo Gamatare
Ho Hamjo Ne Vhali Vat Mari Nathi Het Ma Khot
Papan Na Palalo Vhali Hasta Rakho Hoth
Aa Sakhiyo Hare Manakho Maro
Abhagiyo Aa Bhav Maro
Tu Halyo Gamatre
Ho Aanhude Na Tame Antar Balo
Hasata Modhe Amne Valavo

https://Shakira.lnk.to/followFI

Lyrics

[Intro]
Oooeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeehh!
Viva Africa (Otra, otra)
Viva Africa (Otra, otra)
Viva Africa (Otra, otra)
Viva Africa (Otra, otra)

[Verse 1: Shakira]
You're a good soldier, choosing your battles
Pick yourself up and dust yourself off, get back in the saddle
You're on the front line, everyone's watching
You know it's serious, we're getting closer, this isn't over

[Pre-Chorus: Shakira]
The pressure's on, you feel it
But you got it all, believe it
When you fall get up, oh, oh
If you fall get up, eh, eh
Tsamina mina zangalewa
'Cause this is Africa

[Chorus: Shakira]
Tsamina mina, eh, eh
Waka waka, eh, eh
Tsamina mina zangalewa
This time for Africa

[Verse 2: Shakira]
Listen to your God, this is our motto
Your time to shine, don't wait in line, y vamos por todo
People are raising their expectations
Go on and feed them, this is your moment, no hesitations

[Pre-Chorus: Shakira]
Today's your day, I feel it
You paved the way, believe it
If you get down get up, oh, oh
When you get down get up, eh, eh
Tsamina mina zangalewa
This time for Africa

[Chorus: Shakira]
Tsamina mina, eh, eh
Waka waka, eh, eh
Tsamina mina zangalewa
Anawa-a-a
Tsamina mina, eh, eh
Waka waka, eh, eh
Tsamina mina zangalewa
This time for Africa

[Verse 3: Zolani]
Awabuye lamajoni, ipikipiki mama wa A to Z
Bathi susa lamajoni, ipikipiki mama from East to West
Bathi waka waka mah, eh, eh
Waka waka mah, eh, eh
Zonk' izizwe mazibuye
'Cause this is Africa

[Bridge]
Tsamina mina, Anawa-a-a
Tsamina mina
Tsamina mina, Anawa-a-a

[Chorus: Shakira]
Tsamina mina, eh, eh
Waka waka, eh, eh
Tsamina mina zangalewa
Anawa-a-a
Tsamina mina, eh, eh
Waka waka, eh, eh
Tsamina mina zangalewa
This time for Africa

[Post-Chorus: Shakira]
Django, eh, eh
Django, eh, eh
Tsamina mina zangalewa
Anawa-a-a
Django, eh, eh
Django, eh, eh
Tsamina mina zangalewa
Anawa-a-a

[Outro: Shakira]
This time for Africa
This time for Africa
We're all Africa (Zama qhela)
We're all Africa (Kwela kwela)
Zama qhela

INDIA VS ENGALND Test 4 Day 2 Preview ;.

England leads the Anderson-Tendulkar Trophy 2-1 Ravindra Jadeja broke the mammoth opening stand by dismissing Zak Crawley. Anshul Kamboj managed to make a breakthrough late in the day picking up his maiden Test wicket by dismissing Duckett, but England ended Day 2 at a commanding 225/2 ‚Äî just 133 behind.

Earlier, India‚Äôs innings was boosted by Rishabh Pant‚Äôs courageous 54 despite a fractured toe, and handy lower-order runs from Sundar (27) and Thakur (41). Ben Stokes was the pick of the bowlers, claiming 5/72 ‚Äî his first Test five-wicket haul since 2017.
